sections.Trivia:
- The bus at the beginning is the same from The Mysterious Passenger.
- The vehicles at the place where the victim fell are a 2008 blue Honda Inspire [CP3] and a 2003 polar white Mercedes-Benz CLK 320 [A209].
- Hirukawa's friends' vehicle is a 2004 Toyota Prius II [NHW20].
- The suspects' names come from "hotel chains"[1] :
Toshiko Hirukawa (昼川 利子) comes from Hilton Hotels (ヒルトンホテル ,Hiruton Hoteru?) ;
Teigo Uesumi (上住 貞伍) comes from Westin Hotels (ウェスティンホテル ,Wesutin Hoteru?).
